{"tid":1847863,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有黃店懷疑出售次貨口罩","createTime":"2020-01-28T08:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T11:28:28.000Z","uid":125349,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bb7567fe734df3ef3b4871ebe7127e90866eb754","tid":1847863,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:41:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pepelovehk/photos/a.127746125284741/196782258381127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpepelovehk%2Fphotos%2Fa.127746125284741%2F196782258381127&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb5riIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=585d3fed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pepelovehk/photos/a.127746125284741/196782258381127</a><br />\n有關黃店聲稱口罩<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有齊驗證已查</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dECf07D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdECf07D.png&h=6d184403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n翻查官網，只係見到得前層<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只有 BFE 97-98% 認證，成個口罩並無任何病毒相關認證 (VFE PFE ASTM) 及其數據</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nqAUxeZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnqAUxeZ.png&h=9da4a71e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPPSpunbonded 14g/m&sup2; at front.<br />\nFilter 25g/m&sup2;<span style=\"color: red;\"> (BFE 97-98%) </span>at middle.<br />\nES Thermalbonded 20g/m&sup2; at back.<br />\nPP Thermalbonded 20g/m&sup2; at edge.<br />\n50 pcs / box, 12 boxes / case<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請落單手足小心選購。</span></span>"},{"pid":"13ee52de94e6d01858a5755a017fb0d19546b048","tid":1847863,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:42:08.000Z","msg":"推 1"},{"pid":"4e2f6c5c8fa62695338c7bb143101f3083c4075a","tid":1847863,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy